   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Twenty-nine EVERYONE WHO BELIEVES IN HIM</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>SHALL RECEIVE FORGIVENESS OF SINS Scripture: Acts 10:43 All are sinners Man has sinful deeds.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Man is under condemnation.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Jesus is the Savior Jesus is God incarnated to be the Savior of man.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>He died on the cross for our sins.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>He resurrected from the dead and His resurrection became the basis of our faith.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Believe in Jesus To believe in Jesus is to believe that He is the Son of God.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Believe that He resurrected from the dead.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Believe all the words of the Scripture.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>In spirit receive Him as your Savior.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>The result of believing in the Lord Your sins are forgiven.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>The assurance of the forgiveness of sins is found in this verse: Everyone who believes in Him shall receive forgiveness of sins.</S>
   </TEXT>
